Peter   Nakada CFAProduct Specialist, Stone Ridge Asset Management LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 1 different industries.----
Background

		Mr. Peter Nakada, CFA serves as a Product Specialist at Stone Ridge Asset Management LLC. Mr. Nakada served as Managing Director of Risk Markets of Risk Management Solutions, Inc. He served as Managing Director and Senior Vice President of RMS Consulting. Mr. Nakada was responsible for business development and client service delivery for the consulting business at RMS. Prior to joining RMS, he co-founded ERisk, where he played various roles including head of R&D and ... consulting. Before that, Mr. Nakada served as a director in Oliver, Wyman & Company's Risk Management and Insurance practices. His experience includes enterprise risk and capital management, shareholder value optimization, asset/liability management, and active portfolio management with property & casualty insurers, life insurers, and banks in North America, Europe, and the emerging markets. Mr. Nakada is a Member of Board of Trustees at The Speyer Legacy School. He has authored many articles on risk and is a frequent conference speaker. Mr. Nakada has a B.A. in Engineering Sciences from Harvard College, a M.S. in Engineering Management from Stanford University and is a Chartered Financial Analyst.Read Full Background




